00:09:41.850 --> 00:09:42.580
Doha-hyung.

00:09:42.850 --> 00:09:44.850
¿Por qué estabas parado afuera?

00:09:45.650 --> 00:09:47.970
Oh, um, pareces ocupado.

00:09:49.620 --> 00:09:50.320
Por cierto,

00:09:51.270 --> 00:09:52.100
¿acaso tú?

00:09:53.350 --> 00:09:54.750
